---
const highlights = [
  'Comptes Instagram artisans & créateurs',
  'Avant / après — résultats mesurables',
  'Contenus adaptés à chaque savoir-faire',
];
---

<section class="py-20 px-6 md:px-12 border-t border-[#D6CCC0] bg-[#EDE6DB]">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-12">

    <!-- Texte -->
    <div class="md:w-1/2 space-y-6">
      <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-[#2C2416] tracking-tight">Avant / Après</h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-[#2C2416]/70 leading-relaxed">
        Chaque compte raconte une transformation. Un artisan invisible qui devient visible. Un savoir-faire qui trouve enfin ses clients. Les résultats avant/après arrivent prochainement.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 pt-4">
        {highlights.map(item => (
          <li class="flex items-center text-[#2C2416]/80">
            <iconify-icon icon="solar:check-circle-linear" stroke-width="1.5" class="mr-3 text-lg text-[#767A55]"></iconify-icon>
            {item}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
      <div class="pt-6">
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="px-8 py-3 bg-transparent border border-[#2C2416] text-[#2C2416] rounded-full hover:bg-[#2C2416] hover:text-[#F5EDE4] transition-all duration-300 inline-block"
        >
          Me contacter
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mockup carte -->
    <div class="md:w-1/2 relative">
      <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-[#D6CCC0] p-8 flex flex-col justify-between rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
          <div class="w-1/3 h-4 bg-[#EDE6DB] rounded"></div>
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#F5EDE4] rounded-full border border-[#D6CCC0]"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="w-full h-px bg-[#EDE6DB]"></div>
          <div class="w-3/4 h-3 bg-[#EDE6DB] rounded"></div>
          <div class="w-5/6 h-3 bg-[#EDE6DB] rounded"></div>
          <div class="w-2/3 h-3 bg-[#EDE6DB] rounded"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-8">
          <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-[#8B3E22] text-white text-xs rounded">Avant / Après</div>
          <span class="text-[#D6CCC0] text-4xl font-serif italic">Bientôt.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
